## 解説

小さい数 `d` から割り切れる回数だけ `d` を出力します。`d * d <= n` まで調べ、最後に残った N が 1 より大きければ、それ自体が（最大の）素因数です。

```cpp
bool first = true;
for (int d = 2; (long long)d * d <= n; d++)
    while (n % d == 0) { if (!first) cout << " "; cout << d; first = false; n /= d; }
if (n > 1) { if (!first) cout << " "; cout << n; }
cout << "\n";
```

answer_code:
#include <bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;

int main() {
    int n;
    cin >> n;
    bool first = true;
    for (int d = 2; (long long)d * d <= n; d++)
        while (n % d == 0) { if (!first) cout << " "; cout << d; first = false; n /= d; }
    if (n > 1) { if (!first) cout << " "; cout << n; }
    cout << "\n";
    return 0;
}
